        My scoring methodology [to be further filled in]: I _do_ give "perfect" reviews, if I feel 
        that a book realistically couldn't have been done better. For example, as a movie trilogy, 
        The Lord of the Rings deserves a "perfect" score for many reasons.
    </p>

